text: Elikkattoor is a village in the Kollam district. It is in the Indian state of Kerala. It is near Punalur. == Politics == Elikkattoor is a part of Punalur assembly constituency in Kollam (Lok Sabha constituency). K. Raju is the current MLA of Punalur. N. K. Premachandran is the current member of parliament of Kollam. == References == Category:Villages in Kollam district
title: Elikkattoor
